description: Serving up Hebrew National hot dogs cooked to perfection, and our ice shavers with a mixture of 15 different flavors including Blue Raspberry, Root Beer, or Lemonade as well as our signature mixtures like Morning Sunrise, Over the Rainbow and Baboon Butt! Available for private parties, corporate events or just about any event. You'll love our beach theme and the look and taste will keep you coming back.
name: Dude's Dog Shack and Ice Shavers
